\end_inset

 is UMP with 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\alpha & =P_{\theta_{0}}\left(\bar{X}<x_{0}\right)\\
 & =\frac{n}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\int_{-\infty}^{x_{0}}e^{-\frac{n}{2}\left(x-\theta_{0}\right)^{2}}dx
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $H_{1}:\theta\neq\theta_{0}$
