 & =\frac{n}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\int_{x_{0}}^{\infty}e^{-\frac{n}{2}\left(x-\theta_{0}\right)^{2}}dx
\end{align*}

\end_inset

Both of these cannot be satisfied at the same time, i.e.
 reject if 
